						<h3>Anxiety</h3>
						<p>Anxiety disorders encompass excessive worry, fear, or nervousness, often accompanied by physical symptoms like restlessness and difficulty concentrating. Conditions such as generalised anxiety disorder, social anxiety, and panic disorder fall under this category.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

