							<p>Excessive worry, restlessness, muscle tension, difficulty concentrating, sleep disturbances.</p>
						</li>
						<li class="sub-heading">
							<h3>Causes:</h3>
							<p>Genetics, brain chemistry, environmental stressors, traumatic experiences.</p>
						</li>
						<li class="sub-heading">
							<h3>Types:</h3>
							<p>Generalised anxiety disorder, panic disorder, social anxiety disorder.</p>
						</li>
						<li class="sub-heading">
							<h3>Ways to Heal:</h3>
							<p>Cognitive-behavioural therapy, medication, relaxation techniques, mindfulness.</p>
						</li>
					</ul>
					<h5>You Can Overcome Anxiety. It Does Not Have To Stay That Way.</h5>
